metadata.name: GangApeBlingClub #1
metadata.description: 5,555 Gang PFP, we just want to quickly reach and connect people who are passionate about Hip Hop.   We have taken the inspiration from the streetwear and Hip-Hop culture, the whole 5,555 Apes GANG have 200+special meticulously hand-painted traits of Hip Hop style.   Gang Ape Bling Club is not only a Bling club but also a Hip-Hop ecosystem; Game, Music, Fashion, Stake and Party!
